g": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 选定*", "timestamp": 1603979193, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 500394, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "现在官僚治国，人治而非法治的“文化遗产”不是被发扬光大佬吗", "timestamp": 1603979211, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 500401, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "*了吗", "timestamp": 1603979258, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 500419, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "说句不好听的话，江能让位给胡完全是因为屈服于邓的威望吧？", "timestamp": 1603979437, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 500423, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 确实", "timestamp": 1603979490, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 500424, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "邓开了冠冕堂皇人治的头", "timestamp": 1603979514, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 500450, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "极权主义的诱惑", "timestamp": 1603979992, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 500463, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "甚至可以说邓 江对于中国法治化的发展起了很大的阻碍作用", "timestamp": 1603980119, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 500504, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 同意", "timestamp": 1603980941, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 500508, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 极权社会就不可能有真正法制，因为司法独立是不被允许的。", "timestamp": 1603981106, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 500527, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 信口开河", "timestamp": 1603981567, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 501055, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 异议 真人其实是当时飘了 想梭哈一把 借运动自己上位", "timestamp": 1603988319, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 501238, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 104141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 对，但是其实运动发展到那个时候，早就成了保守派和改革派政治斗争的筹码，真人当然不例外", "timestamp": 1603990593, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 104141, "reply": 21, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "#政治相关\n越来越觉得80年代邓在政治上的一些改革，从现在来看是非常值得诟病的\n邓不想让党内再出现一个毛式的集权人物，于是在宪法中加入了任期制，但是最重要的军委主席的职位却不设任期制度。是因为他自己当时是军委主席的私心缘故吗？\n很多政治上的限制仅仅停留在政治惯例的层面，没有公开立法成文，这也就给后面留了很大的空子，江在任期满之后强行续2年军委主席就是例子？\n而且邓完全不从自身开始做榜样，在辞去所有职务后还利用自身影响力南巡干涉政务。现在感觉，邓时代以来权力的交接依赖的完全是邓自身的威信而不是落实的制度", "timestamp": 1603978812, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782639, "url": "", "vote": {}}}